reviewText: I had watched the Telenovela and wondered about the original movie version.  I was not disappointed the story line was the same only set in the 1960's.  I loved it!

I chose this movie because I love the 60's Mexican movies.  They don't make them like they use to.  Now it's a Spanish soap opera remake (telenovela). The modern version telenovela is more detailed, yet the movie generates flashbacks of my youth.
